videos.title: Bridgeport Biking Trails TX 2020
videos.description: we found this awesome bike trail hidden in Bridgeport Texas where we were staying at Bay Landing thousand trails RV resort. There was some rain that happened and we weren't able to ride this trail as much as we wanted but we got to ride it a few times and it is a great trail to ride through the woods and get some nature.
